Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:18.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:30.22,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:36.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:42.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:48.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:52.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:58.08,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:01.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:06.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:12.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:17.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:24.12,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:36.75,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(85,142)}LONELY SONG
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:55.28,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Some two years have passed\Nsince the fierce battle between the Earth UN Forces\Nand the Bodol main fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:14.98,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:19.44,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.29,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:26.93,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then BOOM! he makes a sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:32.46,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving a long trail of vapor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:37.16,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The few that survived have\Nrisen up from despair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:42.94,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and have gradually returned to\Na peaceful, civilian way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:05.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I've had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:13.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:16.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop it! Just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.05,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:22.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had it with this stupid crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:23.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sayin' {\i1}rigzinalo{\i0} to this dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, {\i1}utema{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:36.59,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to adapt to life on Earth and\Nnot knowing to do with their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:41.57,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,the number of disgruntled Zentradi\Ngrows larger each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And here she is, Miss Lynn Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Minmay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:20.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Once more from the top, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:43.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And my apologies for calling you\Ndown here when you're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:46.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like I'm not going\Nto like this report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:50.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When you hear the conclusion that I and\Nthe staff and have reached, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were terrible out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes me worried about the\Ncharity concert tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing fine tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:15.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There just weren't many people in the audience\Ntonight and it threw me a little at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:19.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an exclusive restaurant.\NIt's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:23.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have lowered my\Nperformance fee a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:26.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We should take money from\Nthose who have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:32.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're sharing it with those\Nwho aren't so fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're even donating half of the proceeds\Nfrom the charity concert tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:41.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, why don't we just donate all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, we're professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural that you\Nshould be paid to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:51.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But we already have plenty of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:54.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not enough to make\Nour dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:01.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we promise that we'd build\Na big concert hall together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:04.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, take off that makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we go treat ourselves\Nto some good food, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:16.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'm singing for anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:20.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense.\NI'll bring the car around back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you hungry for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I want to go to Nyan-Nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To my dad's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:47.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always on tour, so I haven't\Nbeen back there at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:08.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I'll go by myself if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:15.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think of something.\NAnd I'll be back in time for the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine. I'll take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But just to the edge of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:24.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.81,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Dad my best when you see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:42.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on this data, we have concluded that if\Nwe trace our origins back to their source
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:47.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth people and Zentradi are\Nvirtually identical species.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:55.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It is almost certain that both Earth people\Nand Zentradi are descendants of the Protoculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:03.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In going over all the data and examining\Nour respective roots, we found one shared trait after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:07.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One of these in particular exhibits\Na high degree of commonality:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:19.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that we both enjoy waging war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:23.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:29.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at the very least, we humans\Ndon't fight because we enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:33.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we come under attack, we'll fight\Nto protect ourselves, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.83,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a rationalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:43.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans have waged war on one another\Nfor all of recorded history, long before the attack from outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There has always been a war\Nsomewhere on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity is clearly a belligerent species.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:56.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think your numbers and other data\Nare distorting the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers do not lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We are here today to report the\Ndata from our analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:05.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep your personal opinions out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:06.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:14.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, what could have caused\Nnearly identical species to split into humanity and Zentradi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:18.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that going forward, that will\Nbe the focus of our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:25.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.\NAs to what future our way of life will lead to,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot be certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't care what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:33.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's no way that humans will\Nend up like the Zentradi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:40.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:43.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but don't you have to work today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! How's your job going, Mr. Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:52.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's goin' great, thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:57.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle, I was hoping I could\Nimpose on you for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What're ya talkin' about?\NThis place is your home, Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Warms your heart, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:09.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay may be a celebrity now,\Nbut she hasn't changed a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.50,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That makes it sound like\NI haven't grown up at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, that ain't the case, neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:24.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:30.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:51.81,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What... What am I even singing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:56.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Minmay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"You in there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Hikaru? Is that you, Hikaru?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:46.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Minmay, I'm sorry about today."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:50.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"You couldn't help it.\NAfter all, you're a soldier."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:54.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"And about your present..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:05.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Wow, it's so pretty!\NI can really have this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:06.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Yeah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:14.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Minmay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:58.81,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,G'morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lynn Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:24.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Loli! Gimme a hand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:26.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I've got news! Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:27.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Conda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Minmay's back at Nyan-Nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:31.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:34.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! I heard it over at the Mayor's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:38.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But Minmay has a concert tonight\Nin Stone City, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If she leaves this morning,\Nshe'll make it with time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:44.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! If I'd known, I would have\Ngone to eat at Nyan-Nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:52.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't on her private schedule...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Loli! We aren't a bunch\Nof gossip columnists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:59.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We run an upstanding laundry\Nbusiness! Now get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, could...\Ncould you autograph these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Warera, those belong to\Nour customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:22.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just buy 'em new ones, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!\NAll right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!\NHey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You, wait!\NNo, me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:27.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:38.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just go flyin' off\Nthe handle like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Zentradi have suddenly\Ngone on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:51.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! They're trying to take our food\Nor something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:57.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was she talking to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't try goin' against 'em like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Major Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:17.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you out so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:21.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You were as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:32.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Being out with my patrol unit sort of\Nmakes me worry about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:34.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least I'm getting some\Njogging in while I'm at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:38.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, the city seems restless somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:41.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hope we don't get\Na big riot or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:42.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:48.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Major, I put those pictures of you in my album.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:48.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't take it the wrong way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,M... Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:01.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:16.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:23.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Li'l Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:25.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had it with all this work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:31.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I told ya, if you're unhappy,\Nwe'll listen to what ya have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If they start gettin' crazy,\Nthere ain't nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you resist, we will use lethal force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Dern! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:06.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're having trouble living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The military government will\Nlisten to your complaints!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:14.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, all of you! If you really\Nwant what's best for us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,send us back to the Zentradi forces right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,B... But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fight a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:24.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:31.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us fight a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:38.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee that the Zentradi\Nwon't attack the Earth again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's impossible right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:45.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, then quit talkin' to us\Nlike you actually care!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:19.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to think that\Nculture was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:23.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come because Lynn Minmay's\Nsongs moved you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you stick with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've worked so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:43.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we'll be seeing more Zentradi\Nwho can't adjust to life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:46.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What will they do now that they've run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:50.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Starve to death. Or steal from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? More of them have wandered off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:11.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. According to our information,\Ndisgruntled elements have been
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:14.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,quitting their jobs in cities all over and\Nby now may number over 10,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:20.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So waiting in this hellhole for the past\Ntwo years has been worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:29.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone got all carried away by this "culture"\Nthing, but their excitement didn't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:33.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:40.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, we can create a force that will\Ngive those earth people a rather nasty shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Find everyone who's left the cities\Nand bring them back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:53.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no more sneaking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:54.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We move now in broad daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:59.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And tell whoever's been micloned\Nthat if they join Lord Kamujin,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:01.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,he will restore them to their former state!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Long live Kamujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kaifun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Minmay be much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's on in ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:34.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be here! She would never\Nblow off an engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:38.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be so, but she's supposed to be\Nhere thirty minutes before showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a promoter when this\Nis all the people you can get?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:45.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:53.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:55.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't as many in the\Naudience as we'd expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how many\Npeople there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sing better than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:12.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sing my songs for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sing my songs..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"for myself"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E! Lovely Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:27.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E! Lovely Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:31.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E! Lovely Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:37.12,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:37.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What I am about to say is part\Nof a top-secret project.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:42.21,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Love drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:41.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:42.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:47.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, we finally located the\NZentradi Factory Satellite, an automated plant for the\Nconstruction of space vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:53.72,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing before me, a sad look on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:53.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This satellite is able to build spaceships\Ncompletely autonomously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:22:04.92,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're going off to war
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:00.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go and capture that factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:06.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zentradi forces may well come\Nto attack us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:16.13,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,All the men, together, as if possessed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:12.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of our defense, we must obtain\Nas many spacecraft as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:15.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:22.93,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,With mouths pulled tight, with eyes burning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:28.64,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,They march in step
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:40.07,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'll be left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:45.78,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,All for war
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:51.28,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,All for pride
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:57.59,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:03.18,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Love drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:14.87,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I rot away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:34.40,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(88,110)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:34.40,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(341,457)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:45.38,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru and the others, having organized\Na joint force with Britai, depart on an expedition to capture\Nthe Zentradi Factory Satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.13,0:23:53.21,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Max and Milia also elect to bring Maria,\Ntheir baby daughter, along on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:57.61,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:24:02.07,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(88,133)}VIVA MARIA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:23:59.61,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"VIVA MARIA"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.33,0:24:22.48,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:29.04,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.90,0:24:35.75,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.24,0:24:43.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.25,0:24:49.87,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.97,0:24:56.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.82,0:25:04.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.40,0:25:15.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
